.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: poker, monopoly
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, february
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, grey
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who likes grey is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
5. the person playing poker is the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | poker    | monopoly |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Birthday   | july     | february   |
| Color           | amber         | grey    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

