The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, american
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, spy
2 different pets are kept: hamster, pony
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, card-games
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | 7up          | milk       |
| Birthday          | july   | march   |
| Nationality           | american   | italian     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | spy        |
| Pet           | hamster      | pony       |
| Sport         | rowing       | water-polo |
| Hobby     | woodworking          | card-games |

